my energies into that.

564
00:42:31,320 --> 00:42:34,835
Well, l got started later.
Just never met the right girl.

565
00:42:35,720 --> 00:42:37,517
What should a girl
look for in a man?

566
00:42:38,480 --> 00:42:40,835
-Miss Clark?
-What work did you do, Sir?

567
00:42:41,120 --> 00:42:44,556
l waited tables.
l cooked in a hamburger joint.

568
00:42:44,840 --> 00:42:47,070
l washed dishes for a time, cars.

569
00:42:47,680 --> 00:42:50,319
For a year l was a janitor
in an apartment block.

570
00:42:50,600 --> 00:42:52,352
