587
00:43:55,280 --> 00:43:56,349
...the selfish...

588
00:43:56,880 --> 00:43:58,074
...or the insecure.

589
00:44:00,760 --> 00:44:02,193
What's the matter, Weston?

590
00:44:02,480 --> 00:44:04,118
These damn fool Americans!

591
00:44:04,400 --> 00:44:06,994
They bog up everything
they're connected with.

592
00:44:07,280 --> 00:44:08,554
What a shower!

593
00:44:09,400 --> 00:44:13,075
