666
00:51:00,200 --> 00:51:02,794
-That's all right.
-lt's no trouble.

667
00:51:03,080 --> 00:51:06,311
You should get a flat nearby.
Brentwood's much too far away.

668
00:51:06,600 --> 00:51:08,875
-There's nice ones around.
-l've thought of it.

669
00:51:09,160 --> 00:51:11,879
l tell you what.
l'll keep my ears open for you.

670
00:51:12,520 --> 00:51:14,670
That's kind of you,
but l'm fine.

671
00:51:14,960 --> 00:51:16,837
l'll let you know.
Thank you.

672
00:51:18,480 --> 00:51:21,711
Don't worry about your desk.
l'll tidy it for you every day.

673
00:51:22,000 --> 00:51:24,514
